{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't safe at all anymore, from one moment to the next.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was engaged to a wonderful man, the young Herbert Nelson, from The Nelson Review, where I worked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was only half Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His father was full Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His mother was not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said that it would perhaps help me a great deal, because I certainly was on their list-- try to get an Aryan father.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If somebody could get me an Aryan father, that I'm also only half Jewish, it may save me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what happened then before, that was right after my arrest, when really, situations started getting a bit dangerous for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To write-- my mother should write to Budapest to my aunt there, also, of course, in code, that, bottom line, she had an affair when papa was in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had an affair with someone there, and out of this affair came I.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, the first time my fiance suggested that, my mother slapped his face and walked out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So there was no way of her ever writing a letter like this to my aunt, or even suggesting that-- you know, papa would turn in his grave if he knew, and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After it was very dangerous for me, she finally decided, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said to her, you know, papa would understand, and this is not about morality.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is about life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She wrote to my aunt, and thank God she did understand what this was all about.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my wonderful, wonderful cousin went out on the hunt, trying to buy me an Aryan father.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
